00:08:49.750 --> 00:08:52.040
I said mom, I'm going
to tell you something,

00:08:52.040 --> 00:08:55.160
I'm not going to do
it, I'm not going.

00:08:55.160 --> 00:08:57.160
You know she laughed right?

00:08:57.160 --> 00:08:59.920
She said you better
get dressed, stop that.

00:08:59.920 --> 00:09:03.260
I'm like no, I really
mean it, I'm not, I'm not.

00:09:03.260 --> 00:09:05.260
And she said yes you are.

00:09:05.260 --> 00:09:09.840
So you know I don't bugger
too much but, I acted out.

00:09:09.840 --> 00:09:13.170
I moved like molasses I was
hoping that I would move so slow

00:09:13.170 --> 00:09:16.680
