asthma [laughter].

00:09:29.570 --> 00:09:37.140
So I sat up there and I mustered
up an asthma attack, oh yes I did,

00:09:37.140 --> 00:09:40.630
I did it I went [laughter].

00:09:42.150 --> 00:09:43.650
Until I couldn't catch my breath.

00:09:43.650 --> 00:09:51.590
So by the time we got off
the subway, I, here I am.

00:09:51.590 --> 00:09:52.890
Mom [laughter].

00:09:52.890 --> 00:10:01.000
I can't [heavy breathing] you know
we know our children [laughter].

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:04.610
My mother looked across the
street at the drug store

00:10:04.610 --> 00:10:06.410
and she said you see that
drug store over there?

00:10:06.410 --> 00:10:08.980
We're going to go over there, get
that Primatene mist [laughter].

00:10:08.980 --> 00:10:14.320
Now you know Primatene mist you
can get, back in those days,

00:10:14.320 --> 00:10:16.540
