you're going to get on that stage

00:10:16.540 --> 00:10:18.510
and do what you're supposed
to do you know all that.

00:10:18.510 --> 00:10:22.050
So I just said well boy
it's over now [laughter].

00:10:22.050 --> 00:10:25.160
I got to get well and I got to
get up on that stage and I did.

00:10:25.160 --> 00:10:29.970
And it was that Sunday,
that a man came to my mom

00:10:29.970 --> 00:10:34.110
