there are thousands of girls.

00:10:55.580 --> 00:10:59.200
I'm like wow.

00:10:59.200 --> 00:11:03.000
So anyway, you know I knew not
to act up because you know,

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:04.730
the day before wasn't
so good for me.

00:11:04.730 --> 00:11:11.350
So anyway, [laughter] I sat there
and I started thinking to myself,

00:11:11.350 --> 00:11:15.010
and I said, I thought about
something my dad always said.

00:11:15.010 --> 00:11:17.520
What's for you, no
one can take from you

00:11:17.520 --> 00:11:20.440
and I kept saying that
and saying that.

00:11:20.440 --> 00:11:25.350
So when they called me in,
I see Norman sitting there,

00:11:25.350 --> 00:11:28.010
