knew how to improvise.

00:12:04.500 --> 00:12:07.830
So he looked at me and he
said, yes, go ahead improvise.

00:12:07.830 --> 00:12:09.800
You know he's got hundreds
of girls auditioning.

00:12:09.800 --> 00:12:15.400
So anyway I get up there and I
