00:12:31.200 --> 00:12:33.100
so I'm not doing anything.

00:12:33.100 --> 00:12:35.050
So I, we were going back
and forth, back and forth,

00:12:35.050 --> 00:12:38.500
so I hit him, I did, I hit him.

00:12:38.500 --> 00:12:39.800
I hit my brothers.

00:12:39.800 --> 00:12:43.620 position:56%
So I hit him on the arm and he goes,

00:12:43.620 --> 00:12:47.180
you know that long face he makes
that, and so we go back and forth

00:12:47.180 --> 00:12:48.870
and Norman starting laughing.

00:12:48.870 --> 00:12:52.550
So I, after that audition I didn't
hear anything back from them

00:12:52.550 --> 00:12:55.170
for like two months so after two
months you just say well okay

00:12:55.170 --> 00:12:56.860
it's over.

00:12:56.860 --> 00:12:58.900
And after two months
