00:15:02.020 --> 00:15:04.130
She said, why?

00:15:04.130 --> 00:15:05.510
What do you want from, what?

00:15:05.510 --> 00:15:07.960
I said I just want to
become, I loved her,

00:15:07.960 --> 00:15:09.270
